Author: barbie12312
Text: I really do much. I’ve been endlessly binging for about a few months now and I’ve gained some weight. It feels like my body isn’t mine anymore, but I have finals coming up and stressing makes me binge even more.   I wish I can go back to last year when I was so obsessed with losing weight and studied more to forget get about eating.   Now I gained weight and apparently stupidity :)
